      <h3 class="research-title">Labour Market of Ukraine 2022–2023: State, Trends and Prospects</h3>
      <div class="research-meta">
        EBRD-supported analytical report <span class="dot">•</span> 2023 <span class="dot">•</span> National labour market assessment
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="research-row">
    <a class="research-cover" href="/files/en/ebrd-labour-market-2023.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
